data.description: New, bright and spacious property in sought after community. Close to restaurants, schools, parks, shopping and all the best Covington has to offer. This home offers beautiful details: open concept kitchen, beautiful floors, high ceilings... Formal dining room with French doors, separate living room or perfect office, a spacious family room with electric fireplace. The large kitchen has gorgeous white cabinets, extensive island, pantry and breakfast nook. Upstairs, massive principal bedroom with additional sitting area and beautiful principal bathroom with separate shower/bathtub and his and hers walk-in closet. Three more guest bedrooms, laundry room and full bathroom also upstairs. This home has a wonderful backyard with privacy fence and patio. Two car garage. This new home has a premium location within the community. Do not miss the chance to explore this property, book a tour today!
